      ]
    },
    {
      "pos": [
        6508,
        6683
      ],
      "content": "You <bpt id=\"p1\">[</bpt>set up weekly backups<ept id=\"p1\">](web-sites-backup.md#configure-automated-backups)</ept> of your web app that contains static content that never changes, such as old blog posts or images."
